                    #Downloading XAMPP
- Download XAMPP control panel in your PC.
- After downloading XAMPP, start your actions of module 'Apache' and 'MySQL' in XAMPP control panel.

                    #Downloading the project CodePenguin to you system
- Download .zip file naming the folder as "CodePenguin".
- Extract folder "CodePenguin" in path C:\xampp\htdocs

                    #Creating Database
- Make a database naming it as "codepenguin".
- Create a table naming it as "signupdetails".
- Add 4 rows in naming it as - Id, FullName, EmailId and Password.
